                <mxCell id="TOOL_REC" value="&lt;b&gt;Base-year calibration&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Aligns modeled energy with ESTO.&lt;br&gt;Prevents minor and major differences between modelled energy data and ESTO data in the base year.&lt;br&gt;These are bound to occur but luckily a simple proportional adjustment to the input factors is a clean and easy fix!&lt;div&gt;Should be done across all sector/fuel combinations for the base year.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fillColor=#E6FAF8;strokeColor=#3BA7A2;fontColor=#000000;fontSize=14;" parent="L_TOOL" vertex="1">
