                <mxCell id="3Vn5BuMNg00IzMXtSu-n-81" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Assumptions development&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Aspire to pre-plan all modelling parameters before any modelling is done. However these will likely change throughout the process.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=14;" parent="1" vertex="1">
